  "detailed_description": "Is home design software too professional? Is it too difficult to get started?<br>Try\"CozySpace\"!<br>Here, there is a vast model library that not only allows you to create spaces in various styles but also offers specially designed accessories for gamers, such as large desktops, gaming consoles, ambient lights, and more. Unleash your creativity to build your dream esports room.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/97ffb1a32e19d93ebb795411a2be642c.poster.avif?t=1718790991\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/97ffb1a32e19d93ebb795411a2be642c.webm?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/97ffb1a32e19d93ebb795411a2be642c.mp4?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's like a free blueprint for a real room! <br>New features include irregular blueprints and the ability to create multiple rooms, increasing the fidelity of your room replication!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/1d96ce90d5086ce4f0e437d1da5b4284.poster.avif?t=1718790991\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/1d96ce90d5086ce4f0e437d1da5b4284.webm?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/1d96ce90d5086ce4f0e437d1da5b4284.mp4?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Adjust models freely, even turning off collision mode! In the game, you can adjust the size and color of models, and even turn off collision detection, freeing up the Y-axis for a more flexible design!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/a8e795c0660528ee756fd0811add8643.poster.avif?t=1718790991\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/a8e795c0660528ee756fd0811add8643.webm?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/a8e795c0660528ee756fd0811add8643.mp4?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Use deformable cubes to achieve various layouts!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/df32e24e7745709826331c66d42147ef.poster.avif?t=1718790991\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/df32e24e7745709826331c66d42147ef.webm?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/df32e24e7745709826331c66d42147ef.mp4?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Like listening to music to relax?<br>here in Cozyspace, there's an integrated multi-track audio source. Each track can be adjusted individually, allowing you to configure the most suitable music according to your mood!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/86cfe2cb6435138f3eb1961b1a58f31a.poster.avif?t=1718790991\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/86cfe2cb6435138f3eb1961b1a58f31a.webm?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/86cfe2cb6435138f3eb1961b1a58f31a.mp4?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Don't want to do anything? Just want to chill? <br> Cozyspace is the best choice! Build your cozy mini home and enjoy the cyber sunrise and moonset with your little cat or dog.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/9cc1172f929e7783770b45abf69136bd.poster.avif?t=1718790991\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/9cc1172f929e7783770b45abf69136bd.webm?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524480/extras/9cc1172f929e7783770b45abf69136bd.mp4?t=1718790991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> Currently we are in the Early Access stage, and there will be more features coming in the future, waiting to meet players!",
